00:21:29.050 --> 00:21:30.180
Dia monster!

00:21:30.180 --> 00:21:31.180
Maaf...

00:21:31.320 --> 00:21:32.600
- Hei!
- Tunggu, Luffy!

00:21:33.940 --> 00:21:36.960
